title: SET_ENTITY_IGNORE_REQUEST_CONTROL_FILTER
content:
0x9F7F8D36// SetEntityIgnoreRequestControlFilter
void SET_ENTITY_IGNORE_REQUEST_CONTROL_FILTER(Entity entity, bool ignore);Parameters:entity: The entity handle to ignore the request control filter.ignore: Define if the entity ignores the request control filter policy.It allows to flag an entity to ignore the request control filter policy.
